<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Complete the Deal | KRISHIQ</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        'krishi-green': '#2d6a4f',
                        'krishi-dark': '#1b4332',
                        'krishi-light': '#d8f3dc',
                        'krishi-gold': '#f59e0b',
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100 text-krishi-dark font-sans">

    <nav class="bg-white border-b border-gray-200 py-4 px-[5%] flex justify-between items-center shadow-sm">
        <div class="text-2xl font-black text-krishi-green">KRISHIQ <span class="text-gray-400 font-light">| SECURE DEAL</span></div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold text-gray-500">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></span> 256-bit Encrypted
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto py-12 px-4">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
            
            <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-6">
                
                <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
                        📦 Final Deal Summary
                    </h2>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-6 pb-6 border-b border-gray-100">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1574323347407-f5e1ad6d020b?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=200" class="w-24 h-24 rounded-2xl object-cover">
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold">Premium Sharbati Wheat</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-500">Seller: <span class="text-krishi-green font-bold">Rajesh Kumar</span></p>
                            <p class="text-sm bg-krishi-light/50 px-2 py-1 rounded inline-block mt-2 font-medium">Batch #KR-9920</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 py-6">
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 uppercase font-bold mb-1">Agreed Price</p>
                            <p class="text-xl font-bold">₹2,380 <span class="text-sm font-normal">/ Quintal</span></p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 uppercase font-bold mb-1">Total Quantity</p>
                            <p class="text-xl font-bold">50 Quintals</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6">🚚 Logistics & Pickup</h2>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <label class="flex items-center p-4 border-2 border-krishi-green bg-krishi-light/20 rounded-2xl cursor-pointer">
                            <input type="radio" name="logistics" checked class="w-5 h-5 accent-krishi-green">
                            <div class="ml-4">
                                <p class="font-bold">Self-Pickup (Sangrur Mandi)</p>
                                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">You arrange transport. Loading is free.</p>
                            </div>
                        </label>
                        <label class="flex items-center p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50">
                            <input type="radio" name="logistics" class="w-5 h-5 accent-krishi-green">
                            <div class="ml-4">
                                <p class="font-bold">KRISHIQ Logistics Support</p>
                                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">We find a truck for you (+₹4,500 estimated).</p>
                            </div>
                        </label>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6">💳 Secure Payment</h2>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                        <button class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl hover:border-krishi-green transition">
                            <span class="text-2xl mb-1">📱</span>
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold">UPI / GPay</span>
                        </button>
                        <button class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl hover:border-krishi-green transition">
                            <span class="text-2xl mb-1">🏦</span>
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold">Net Banking</span>
                        </button>
                        <button class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4 border-2 border-krishi-green bg-krishi-light/10 rounded-2xl">
                            <span class="text-2xl mb-1">🛡️</span>
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold">Escrow</span>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="lg:col-span-1">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl border border-gray-100 sticky top-24">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6">Payment Breakdown</h2>
                    <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
                        <div class="flex justify-between text-gray-600">
                            <span>Crop Total (50 qtl)</span>
                            <span class="font-bold text-gray-900">₹1,19,000</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between text-gray-600">
                            <span>KRISHIQ Platform Fee</span>
                            <span class="font-bold text-gray-900">₹450</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between text-gray-600">
                            <span>Loading Charges</span>
                            <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">FREE</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="h-px bg-gray-100 my-4"></div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between text-2xl font-black">
                            <span>Total</span>
                            <span class="text-krishi-green">₹1,19,450</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-2 text-[10px] text-gray-400">
                            <input type="checkbox" checked class="mt-1">
                            <span>I agree to the quality standards and purchase terms of KRISHIQ. I understand that the advance is held in Escrow until quality check.</span>
                        </div>
                        <button class="w-full bg-krishi-green text-white font-black py-5 rounded-2xl shadow-lg shadow-green-900/20 hover:bg-krishi-dark transition transform active:scale-95 text-lg">
                            CONFIRM DEAL & PAY
                        </button>
                        <p class="text-center text-[10px] text-gray-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">
                            No Returns after Mandi Gate Exit
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="text-center py-12 text-gray-400 text-sm italic">
        "Your trust is our harvest." — The KRISHIQ Team
    </footer>

</body>
</html>